embed.title: Staff | Rules
embed.description:
Here are all the staff rules of ***Melbourne Roleplay** :
### - Duty
 You may **ONLY** start your duty if there are 9+ **REAL** players in-game, also, you **use**, your assigned callsign.
### - Off-Duty and Banned Commands
 You may **NOT** use any commands while being off-duty, even if calls are stacking when there are less than 9 real players, also, you may **NOT** use any restricted commands.
### - Chain of Command
 You **MUST** respect the chain of command and respect the orders of you higher-ups except if they try to make you break rule or if the orders are abusive.
### - SPaG (Spelling, Punctuation and Grammar)
 When on-duty, youu **MUST** always use SPaG whether you're patrolling, answering calls or talking with friends/others staff members.
### - Patrol
 When on-duty, you may **NOT** wait for a call with your car parked, by that, I mean that you must patrol around the map.
### - Respect
 You **MUST** always be disrespectful towards everyone in discord and in-game whether you're off or on-duty.
### - Internals Affairs Investigations
 You may **NOT** interfere with any IA Investigations.
### - 4 letters commands
 When you use a command, you **MUST** use 4 letters commands (usernames), for example, execute :to vava and not :to vav.
### - Help Requests
 When there is an active help request, you **MUST** abandon roleplay and get on-duty, also, you may **ONLY** make an help requests if you are the only staff in-game, on-duty or if calls are stacking.

embed.title: Discord Rules
embed.description:
Rule 1 : No Abusive Language in our community chats, if our we find any sort of Abusive Language/Behaviour you will receive a warning and a time out.

Rule 2 : No form of NSFW content will be allowed in our community, the consequence of you posting NSFW material will be a ban from Melbourne Roleplay.

Rule 3 : No form of Advertising your own ERLC private server whether that be in DM‚Äôs or public chat. The consequences for this will be a ban unless Foundership disapproves the ban.

Rule 4 : No excessive spamming in chats, if you delete the spamming we will look at the logs and you will receive your first warning and you will be on time out.

Rule 5 : No excessive pinging of an SHR member, you may ping an SHR member ONCE but only if it is deemed important. The consequence of breaking this rule will be a warning and a time out will be received.

Rule 6 : No form of disrespect is tolerated whether that be discrimination, disrespecting our staff members, or disrespecting our community members. The consequence of breaking this rule will be a warning and a time out will be handed out.

Rule 7 : No Harassing any of our members, these people include staff members and our community members/partners. This harassment can be found in DM‚Äôs or in public chats and if you see any harassment going on instantly open a ticket. The consequence of breaking this rule will be a kick.

Rule 8 : No leaking Personal Information of other people in our community or also formally known as Doxxing. Doxxing will not be permitted in our server and the consequence for doing this action will be an instant ban from our server and a report to discord.

Rule 9 : No lying on your staff application, if we find out you have lied or used AI on your application the consequence will be a warning and a Staff Blacklist may be handed out depending on the severity of the situation.

Rule 10 : No excessive use of Brainrot terms, this could be the saying of Italian Brainrot or the word ‚Äú67‚Äù the consequences for this will be a warning and a time out will likely be received.

Rule 11 : Have fun here at the Melbourne Roleplay community! We have kind hearted staff who always welcome new comers. üôÇ
